## Ceremony Channel

The Swordsman maintains a **ceremony channel** for dual-agent coordination:

### Discovery Protocol

```typescript
// Swordsman initiates discovery
channel.startDiscovery()

// Listen for Mage presence
channel.onMagePresent((mageData) => {
  // Switch to dual-orb mode
  renderer.enableDualOrb()

  // Accept constellation data
  channel.setConstellationHandler((data) => {
    renderer.updateConstellation(data)
  })
})
```

### Ceremony Types

| Ceremony | Trigger | Effect |
|----------|---------|--------|
| Dual Convergence | Orbs overlap | Shared hexagram mutation |
| Hexagram Cast | Hold during convergence | Cast combined hexagram |
| Emoji Cast | Quick convergence | Exchange emoji spells |
| Constellation Wave | Extended overlap | Propagate spell nodes |
| Bilateral Exchange | Trust established | Generate VRC proof |

